{"tid":2254427,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–利用污水調查人口社會狀況","createTime":"2020-10-22T22:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T10:58:56.000Z","uid":38861,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa3b63a7b1e76e018d8cb8962feb6982655b41e","tid":2254427,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T22:43:44.000Z","msg":"日常家中的污水，會排放至污水處理廠作淨化處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFYp9PS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFYp9PS.jpg&h=ef214dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但你有沒有想過，污水其實包含著各式各樣的資料呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）圖中的星星為北京市的中心，而八個英文字母的所在地則為污水處理廠的位置。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMcB0WA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMcB0WA.png&h=0e93a9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有科學家特意從八道污水處理廠拿取未經處理過的污水，檢測裡頭的抗生素濃度（Ref1)，初心是因為出自於人民對抗生素使用的認知不足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZpAw3n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZpAw3n.jpg&h=1af246f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）中國在2017年對11,192個大學生作問卷調查，發現<br />\n<br />\n41%學生認為服食抗生素能夠加快流感治癒速度、<br />\n<br />\n63%學生的家中有抗生素儲備，<br />\n<br />\n56%學生未經醫生許可購買抗生素。<br />\n<br />\n其中913個學生中，有66%因報告疑似流惑徵狀而獲發抗生素。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n流感是由病毒引起，抗生素並不會有助治療，反之濫用抗生素只會助長細菌建立抗性，百害而無一利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）各種抗生素最終會有部份從排泄物的方式排出體外。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29Vsn99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29Vsn99.png&h=81cf1a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而基於各污水處的污水的Ammonium(銨)與附近的住宅人口調查成正比的關係，只要將抗生素在污水中的濃度與人體新陳代謝的比率作出調整，然後再除Ammonium的濃度，就可以獲得各地區市民服用抗生素的大概狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）最後計算結果為:<br />\n<br />\n北京市每1萬人口每日服用約21.9克的抗生素。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dVzNBS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dVzNBS.jpg&h=c958bcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文中作者聲稱，此數據比早前的數據低出70%，判斷中國推行抗生素管理政策後非常有效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而這種利用污水來調查人口社會狀況，學名為Wastewater-based epidemiology (WBE)，不少國家亦都有廣泛使用的報告，其中印度芬蘭等國家亦在污水中找出武肺病毒的存在，而啟動病毒來源追溯程序。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=5628b983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=122cf8fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=f067b6d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0160412018320877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0160412018320877&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=75159738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0160412018320877</a>"},{"pid":"136fab23eeefc255788aff41bf4290e8976bfaa7","tid":2254427,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T22:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303402e5b1fd945b1e5a17295fc3defbf55eea68","tid":2254427,"uid":33477,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T22:49:53.000Z","msg":"由得佢哋濫用抗生素，自己毒死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca67c57057855a4c75e818fffcd6da4475b05bd","tid":2254427,"uid":149908,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T22:55:15.000Z","msg":"嘩，養惡菌"},{"pid":"5a57e985103d964f91b785b0ab9e334767cb7cc8","tid":2254427,"uid":159659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"303402e5b1fd945b1e5a17295fc3defbf55eea68","tid":2254427,"uid":33477,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T22:49:53.000Z","msg":"由得佢哋濫用抗生素，自己毒死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T23:00:31.000Z","msg":"你估菌唔識走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e340037cc12f10a7a8e9234fe591b96e05aa1","tid":2254427,"uid":159659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca67c57057855a4c75e818fffcd6da4475b05bd","tid":2254427,"uid":149908,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T22:55:15.000Z","msg":"嘩，養惡菌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T23:01:52.000Z","msg":"聽大陸同事講佢地周街都有得買抗生素，由細食到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd31fc2d1a54654a5e24912f95a553fb906aef8c","tid":2254427,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T23:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj